experience.description:
Manage Material Testing: 
•	Control the process of apparel/material testing;
•	Collect, distribute and analyze testing data from OSO controlled suppliers; 
•	Continuously up-date fabric reports & databases as needed;
•	Manage the creation & distribution of the seasonal BFTSR for BDO office, VNO office and Uzbekistan/Russian suppliers. This includes managing the seasonal product classification process and assignment of test items for these suppliers.
•	Follow up to ensure the timely receipt of testing reports from BDO office, VNO office and Uzbekistan/Russian suppliers; 
•	Promptly validate and resolve or escalate any FAILED test quality issues or questions;
•	Manage and provide seasonal Random Test reports with key fact findings and action plans, monitor execution;
•	Prepare and provide test results to development teams for future improvement of functionality and design, aesthetic and technological properties and characteristics of the materials; 
•	Conduct correspondence with overseas' offices (China, Bangladesh, Vietnam);
•	Organize testing in contracted laboratories, e.g.  ITS and SGS.
•	Coordinate and control the receipt and shipment of test samples as needed. 
•	Monitor and control the distribution of seasonal material and testing requirements;
•	Track and analyze HQ testing cots and budget.
Manage Garment Wear Testing:
•	Assist in collecting samples for wear testing (warehouse, stores, office);
•	Collect and consolidate reports on seasonal garment wear tests;
•	Support documentation of the garment wear testing process;
